WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.710
Welcome to NUSTutors, your one-stop platform
to find the most suitable tutors for your academic needs.

00:00:06.710 --> 00:00:11.350
In this video, we'll guide you through how
to use the various features of our platform.

00:00:11.350 --> 00:00:12.350
Let's get started!

00:00:12.350 --> 00:00:15.390
First, start by heading over to our website.

00:00:15.390 --> 00:00:17.170
There you will find our homepage.

00:00:17.170 --> 00:00:24.039
If you already have an account with NUSTutors,
click the Login button on the top right to login.

00:00:24.080 --> 00:00:29.390
As a new user, just click on the Sign Up Now
button to sign up for a new account.

00:00:29.390 --> 00:00:37.527
Fill in your email address and password and
click Sign Up.

00:00:37.527 --> 00:00:41.430
Next, you will be redirected to the Onboarding
page.

00:00:41.430 --> 00:00:43.770
This is where you will set up your profile.

00:00:43.770 --> 00:00:48.540
You can add your personal details such as
a profile picture, your name, your level and

00:00:48.540 --> 00:01:01.590
course of study, your availability and a brief
introduction about yourself to attract potential students.

00:01:01.590 --> 00:01:06.330
If you're offering tutoring services, let
us know your availability for sessions, the

00:01:06.330 --> 00:01:10.790
subjects you wish to tutor and your hourly
rate, so that prospective students can be

00:01:10.790 --> 00:01:14.490
better informed about your capabilities.

00:01:14.490 --> 00:01:18.364
Once you're satisfied with your profile, don’t
forget to save your details!

00:01:18.364 --> 00:01:23.080
Don’t worry, you can come back to edit your
profile at any time.

00:01:23.080 --> 00:01:28.400
After we have saved your profile, you will
then be directed to your personalized dashboard page.

00:01:28.400 --> 00:01:33.350
The dashboard page allows you to quickly see
the date, time, and details of each tutoring

00:01:33.350 --> 00:01:35.430
session at a glance.

00:01:35.430 --> 00:01:39.140
Moreover, it also allows you to modify and
attend sessions.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:42.079
For now, there aren’t any tutoring sessions
here yet.

00:01:42.079 --> 00:01:45.529
So let’s get started on booking your first
tutoring session!

00:01:45.529 --> 00:01:50.509
Simply click on the blue “Book a Tutor”
button on the dashboard or the Find Tutors

00:01:50.509 --> 00:01:53.030
tab on the Navbar to get started!

00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:55.810
You will see our list of available tutors.

00:01:55.810 --> 00:01:59.950
Simply browse through our list of tutors and
click the “View Profile” button beside

00:01:59.950 --> 00:02:04.690
the tutors whom you are interested in to find
out more about their teaching methods, hourly

00:02:04.690 --> 00:02:06.930
rate and availabilities.

00:02:06.930 --> 00:02:11.380
When you've found the one that fits your requirements,
hit the "Book Tutor" button beside their name

00:02:11.380 --> 00:02:13.270
to start the booking process.

00:02:13.270 --> 00:02:17.700
Here, you'll input all the necessary details
for your tutoring session.

00:02:17.700 --> 00:02:23.060
Choose the module, date, time, and location
that best fits your schedule and needs.

00:02:23.060 --> 00:02:27.349
Once you are done, click on the “Proceed
to Checkout” button.

00:02:27.349 --> 00:02:32.090
In the event that the tutor offers free tutoring
sessions, the “Proceed to Checkout” button

00:02:32.090 --> 00:02:34.920
will be replaced with a “Book Tutor”
button.

00:02:34.920 --> 00:02:41.209
Just click the “Book Tutor” button and your session will 
be booked immediately, no payment needed!

00:02:41.209 --> 00:02:46.800
After clicking the “Proceed to Checkout”
button, you will see a secure payment gateway

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:51.379
provided by Stripe, a reputable third-party
payment processor.

00:02:51.379 --> 00:03:09.896
Just key in your card details and hit Proceed.

00:03:09.896 --> 00:03:33.209
Alternatively, you may also opt for a faster,
seamless checkout with PayNow.

00:03:33.209 --> 00:03:37.019
Go back to the Dashboard page to see your
new session!

00:03:37.019 --> 00:03:40.500
We understand that plans can change, and we've
got you covered!

00:03:40.500 --> 00:03:45.819
If you need to make any changes to a booking,
you can do it on the Dashboard page.

00:03:45.819 --> 00:03:50.350
Simply head over to your dashboard, locate
the specific booking you wish to modify, click

00:03:50.350 --> 00:03:53.680
the ‘Edit” button to start modifying your
session.

00:03:53.680 --> 00:03:59.500
Update the necessary details, whether it's
the date, time, or location, and save your changes.

00:03:59.500 --> 00:04:01.960
Your booking will be modified immediately.

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:08.340
It's that simple!

00:04:08.340 --> 00:04:12.920
When the time comes for your tutoring session,
access your dashboard and locate the booking

00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:14.860
you wish to attend.

00:04:14.860 --> 00:04:19.070
Click on the "Attend" button beside the session
you wish to attend.

00:04:19.070 --> 00:04:23.169
Once you confirm your attendance, the session
will be marked as attended and removed from

00:04:23.169 --> 00:04:26.949
the dashboard, and the payment will be released
to the tutor.

00:04:26.949 --> 00:04:31.380
From time to time, we understand that you
might want to update your availability, or

00:04:31.380 --> 00:04:34.440
even your course of study or modules you can
teach.

00:04:34.440 --> 00:04:38.280
Don’t worry, you can do so using our edit
profile feature.

00:04:38.280 --> 00:04:43.220
To get started, simply click on your profile
picture and choose "Profile Settings".

00:04:43.220 --> 00:04:53.766
Make the necessary changes to your profile
and click the Save profile button.

00:04:53.766 --> 00:04:56.889
Voilà, your profile is updated!

00:04:56.889 --> 00:05:01.660
To effortlessly stay on top of your payment
history, simply click on your profile picture

00:05:01.660 --> 00:05:03.514
and choose "Payment History."

00:05:03.514 --> 00:05:08.410
There, you can see the list that details all
the payments you have made thus far.

00:05:08.410 --> 00:05:12.330
Do note that payments for free tutoring sessions
do not show up here.

00:05:12.330 --> 00:05:16.699
If you are a tutor, you will see an additional
wallet section where you can withdraw your

00:05:16.699 --> 00:05:23.130
earnings to your bank account.

00:05:23.130 --> 00:05:27.940
When it's time to call it a day, you can logout
by clicking on your profile picture icon and

00:05:27.940 --> 00:05:31.110
selecting “logout”.

00:05:31.110 --> 00:05:41.170
To login again, just fill up the login form
with your email address and password!

00:05:41.170 --> 00:05:45.680
Once logged in, you will automatically be
redirected to the dashboard page.

00:05:45.680 --> 00:05:47.569
Forgotten your password?

00:05:47.569 --> 00:05:50.430
Don’t fret, cause we've got you covered!

00:05:50.430 --> 00:05:54.610
With just a few simple steps, you can reclaim
access to your account.

00:05:54.610 --> 00:06:00.850
To initiate the password recovery process, click on 
 the "Forgot Password" option on the login page.

00:06:00.850 --> 00:06:05.730
Enter the email address linked to your NUSTutors
account, and we'll send you a special email

00:06:05.730 --> 00:06:13.250
containing a unique link.

00:06:13.250 --> 00:06:18.030
Open that email, click on the provided link,
and you'll be directed to a password reset

00:06:18.030 --> 00:06:19.030
page.

00:06:19.030 --> 00:06:28.139
Here, you can choose a new password that meets
your preferences.

00:06:28.139 --> 00:06:32.180
Once you've set your new password and saved
your changes, you can proceed to the login

00:06:32.180 --> 00:06:46.449
page and log in with your new password.

00:06:46.449 --> 00:06:51.190
We hope that this video has given you a brief
overview of the features on our platform,

00:06:51.190 --> 00:06:53.580
and answered some of your burning questions.

00:06:53.580 --> 00:06:58.208
Join us and unlock your academic potential
with NUSTutors today!

